name: Watchers of the Melodic Marsh
description: Hailing from the Bogs of the <Anuran Countryside>, the Watchers of the Melodic Marsh are known far and wide for their affinity with all manner of woodwind. Now serving as caretakers of Mohoan Larvae, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
